==Introduction==
対潜兵装です。<br>
いわゆるアクティブソナーです。性能は残念ながら、ものすごく高くはありません。<br>
それでも、他兵装と組み合わせて、練度の高い駆逐艦で敵潜水艦隊を文字通り駆逐してください！

''An anti-submarine weapon, also called the "active sonar".''<br>
''It doesn't have impressive performance; however, when used in tandem with other equipment, a veteran destroyer will surely put enemy submarines down!''

==Notes==
Ships receive a 15% [[Damage Calculations#Anti-Submarine Warfare|ASW synergy bonus]] when this is used together with a [[:Category:Depth Charge Projectors|depth charge projector]] or [[:Category:Depth Charges|depth charge]]; and a 43% bonus when all three types are used (must be on the same ship). The 43% bonus does not apply when used together with a [[:Category:Special Depth Charge Projectors|special DCP]].

